INFN-LScan version 0.1
======================

This is a decent lightweight md5 directory based file watcher

It is easy to use, check out the help by running lscan -h

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

DBI
File::Find
Digest::MD5

